All Sides is the upcoming sixth studio album by Of A Revolution (O.A.R.), set to be released on July 14, 2008. Two of the tracks, "This Town" and "What is Mine", were posted on the band&#039;s official website and Myspace. The only other known songs on the album are "Living in the End" and "Something Coming Over" which were previously recorded on the band&#039;s last album Live from Madison Square Garden.

Package

With the purchase of two tickets to the "All Sides Tour", you could pre-order an MP3 version of the album and you will be sent the two tracks "This Town" and "What is Mine" immediately after your purchase. The radio single "Shattered" is then sent to you June 13 as are the remaining 10 tracks 24 hours prior to the release of the actual album.
